<ptxt>Select an appropriate flange so that the pack clearance will be within the specified range.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Pack clearance</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt> 0.745 to 1.21 mm (0.0293 to 0.0476 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
