<s-1 id="RM000000YX800FX_01_0009" proc-id="RM0250U___00000Q400000">
<ptxt>INSPECT PACK CLEARANCE OF SECOND BRAKE</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Using vernier calipers, measure the distance between the disc surface and snap ring surface (Dimension B).</ptxt>
