<s-1 id="RM000000YX800FX_01_0010" proc-id="RM0250U___00000Q500000">
<ptxt>INSPECT PACK CLEARANCE OF NO. 2 UNDERDRIVE CLUTCH</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Using a dial indicator, measure the underdrive clutch pack clearance while applying and releasing compressed air (392 kPa, 4.0 kgf/cm<sup>2</sup>, 57 psi). </ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="D008082" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<spec>
<title>Pack clearance</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt> 1.645 to 2.20 mm (0.0648 to 0.0866 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Select an appropriate flange from the table below so that the pack clearance will be within the specified range.</ptxt>
