<s-1 id="RM000000YX800FX_01_0020" proc-id="RM0250U___00006N800000">
<ptxt>INSPECT 2ND BRAKE PISTON RETURN SPRING SUB-ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Using vernier calipers, measure the free length of the spring together with the spring seat.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C089124E02" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<spec>
<title>Standard free length</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>16.61 mm (0.6539 in.)</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the free length is shorter than the standard free length, replace the 2nd brake piston return spring sub-assembly.</ptxt>
</s2>
</content1>
